The Occupation Recalibration

52
00:02:45,818 --> 00:02:47,818
Traduzione: Fry, Mlle Kurtz, Saropula.

53
00:02:55,130 --> 00:02:57,090
Revisione: rikyrich.

54
00:02:57,150 --> 00:02:59,150
